#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Usage"
msgstr "उन्नतप्रयोगः"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Line Options"
msgstr "आदेशपङ्क्तिविकल्पाः"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When running &appname; from the command line, there are several options for "
"opening data files. They may be seen by running <userinput>tellico --help</"
"userinput>. Diagnostic logging can also be enabled, which will make a <link "
"linkend=\"settings-help-menu\">menu item</link> to show the diagnostic log. "
"The <userinput>--logfile</userinput> option redirects the log to a file."
msgstr ""
"यदा &amp;appname; आदेशपङ्क्तौ, दत्तांशसञ्चिकाः उद्घाटयितुं अनेकाः विकल्पाः सन्ति । धावनेन "
"दृश्यन्ते स्यात्<userinput> टेलिको --सहाय</userinput> . निदान-लॉगिंग् अपि सक्षमं कर्तुं "
"शक्यते, यत् क<link linkend=\"settings-help-menu\"> मेनू मद</link> निदानवृत्तं दर्शयितुं "
"। द<userinput> --लॉगसञ्चिका</userinput> विकल्पः लॉगं सञ्चिकां प्रति पुनः निर्दिशति ।"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: advanced.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Usage: tellico [options] [filename]\n"
"\n"
"Tellico - collection management software, free and simple\n"
"\n"
"Options:\n"
"  --nofile                  Do not reopen the last open file\n"
"  --bibtex                  Import &lt;filename&gt; as a bibtex file\n"
"  --mods                    Import &lt;filename&gt; as a MODS file\n"
"  --ris                     Import &lt;filename&gt; as a RIS file\n"
"  --pdf                     Import &lt;filename&gt; as a PDF file\n"
"  --log                     Log diagnostic output\n"
"  --logfile &lt;logfile&gt;       Write log output to &lt;filename&gt;\n"
"\n"
"Arguments:\n"
"  [filename]                File to open"
msgstr ""
"उपयोगः: tellico [विकल्पाः] [सञ्चिकानाम] ।\n"
"\n"
"Tellico - संग्रह प्रबन्धन सॉफ्टवेयर, निःशुल्क सरल च\n"
"\n"
"विकल्पाः : १.\n"
"  --nofile अन्तिमं उद्घाटितं सञ्चिकां पुनः न उद्घाटयन्तु\n"
"  --bibtex आयातं &lt;सञ्चिकानाम&gt; bibtex सञ्चिकारूपेण\n"
"  --mods आयातं कुर्वन्तु &lt;सञ्चिकानाम&gt; MODS सञ्चिकारूपेण\n"
"  --ris आयातं &lt;सञ्चिकानाम&gt; RIS सञ्चिकारूपेण\n"
"  --pdf आयातं &lt;सञ्चिकानाम&gt; PDF सञ्चिकारूपेण\n"
"  --log Log निदाननिर्गमः\n"
"  --लॉगसञ्चिका &lt;लॉगसञ्चिका&gt;       लॉग् आउटपुट् &lt;सञ्चिकानाम&gt;\n"
"\n"
"तर्काः : १.\n"
"  [filename] उद्घाटयितुं सञ्चिका"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "&DBus; Interface"
msgstr "&DBus; अन्तरफलकम्"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&appname; has a minimal &DBus; interface, which can be useful for scripting "
"or interacting with a running application from the command-line. As with all "
"&DBus; calls, you need to specify the service you want to interface with, "
"and the particular interface. The name of the &DBus; service is "
"<constant>org.kde.tellico</constant>."
msgstr ""
"&अप्पनाम; न्यूनतमं &DBus; interface, यत् आदेशपङ्क्तौ चालितेन अनुप्रयोगेन सह स्क्रिप्टिङ्ग् "
"अथवा अन्तरक्रियायै उपयोगी भवितुम् अर्हति । यथा सर्वेषां &DBus; calls, भवन्तः यस्य "
"सेवायाः सह अन्तरफलकं कर्तुम् इच्छन्ति, तथा च विशेषं अन्तरफलकं निर्दिष्टुं आवश्यकम् । नाम "
"&DBus; सेवा <नित्य>org.kde.tellico</constant> इति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "&DBus; Commands"
msgstr "&DBus; आदेशाः"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Two &DBus; primary objects are available in the tellico interface: "
"<constant>Tellico</constant> and <constant>Collections</constant>."
msgstr ""
"द्वे &DBus; प्राथमिकवस्तूनि tellico अन्तरफलके उपलभ्यन्ते: <constant>Tellico</constant> "
"तथा <constant>Collections</constant> ।"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <constant>Tellico</constant> Object"
msgstr "<नित्य>टेलिको</constant> वस्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The full list of &DBus; commands in the <constant>tellico</constant> object "
"is shown below:"
msgstr ""
"&DBus इत्यस्य पूर्णसूची; <constant>tellico</constant> वस्तुनि आदेशाः अधः दर्शिताः "
"सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: advanced.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool importTellico(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool importBibtex(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool importMODS(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool importPDF(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool importRIS(QString file, QString action)\n"
"bool exportXML(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"bool exportZip(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"bool exportBibtex(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"bool exportHTML(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"bool exportCSV(QString file, bool filtered)\n"
"QList&lt;int&gt; selectedEntries()\n"
"QList&lt;int&gt; filteredEntries()\n"
"void openFile(QString file)\n"
"void setFilter(QString text)\n"
"bool showEntry(int id)"
msgstr ""
"bool importTellico (QString सञ्चिका, QString क्रिया)\n"
"bool importBibtex (QString सञ्चिका, QString क्रिया)\n"
"bool importMODS (QString सञ्चिका, QString क्रिया)\n"
"bool importPDF (QString सञ्चिका, QString क्रिया)\n"
"bool importRIS (QString सञ्चिका, QString क्रिया)\n"
"bool exportXML (QString सञ्चिका, bool फ़िल्टर)\n"
"bool exportZip (QString सञ्चिका, bool फ़िल्टर)\n"
"bool exportBibtex (QString सञ्चिका, bool फ़िल्टर)\n"
"bool exportHTML(QString सञ्चिका, bool फ़िल्टर)\n"
"bool exportCSV(QString सञ्चिका, bool फ़िल्टर)\n"
"QList&lt;int&gt; चयनितप्रविष्टयः () .\n"
"QList&lt;int&gt; filteredEntries () 1.1.\n"
"void openFile(QString सञ्चिका)\n"
"void setFilter (QString पाठ) 1.1.\n"
"bool showEntry (int आईडी) 1.1."

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the four import commands, the first argument is the file to import, and "
"the second is the import action. Three actions are available: "
"<emphasis>replace</emphasis>, <emphasis>append</emphasis>, and "
"<emphasis>merge</emphasis>. Four file formats are supported for importing: "
"Tellico &XML; files, Bibtex files, MODS files, and RIS files. Metadata from "
"<link linkend=\"importing-pdf\">&PDF;</link> files can also be imported."
msgstr ""
"चतुर्णां आयात-आदेशानां कृते प्रथमः तर्कः आयातित-सञ्चिका, द्वितीयः आयात-क्रिया । त्रयः "
"कर्माणि उपलभ्यन्ते- १.<emphasis> प्रत्याहृ</emphasis> , ९.<emphasis> append इति</"
"emphasis> , तथा<emphasis> विलयः</emphasis> . आयातार्थं चत्वारि सञ्चिकास्वरूपाणि "
"समर्थितानि सन्ति: Tellico &amp;XML; सञ्चिकाः, Bibtex सञ्चिकाः, MODS सञ्चिकाः, RIS "
"सञ्चिकाः च । मेटाडाटा तः<link linkend=\"importing-pdf\"> &amp;PDF;</link> "
"सञ्चिकाः आयातयितुं अपि शक्यन्ते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For any of the commands to export text, a file name of <filename>--</"
"filename> will pipe to the standard output."
msgstr ""
"पाठस्य निर्यातार्थं कस्यापि आदेशस्य कृते <filename>--</filename> इत्यस्य सञ्चिकानाम "
"मानकनिर्गमं प्रति पाइप् करिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The current open collection in &appname; may be exported to a file, in "
"either Tellico &XML; format, Tellico ZIP format, Bibtex, &HTML;, or comma-"
"separated values (CSV). The export commands take an optional argument to "
"specify whether the collection should be limited to the current filter or "
"not."
msgstr ""
"&appname; सञ्चिकायां निर्यातं कर्तुं शक्यते, Tellico &XML; प्रारूपं, Tellico ZIP प्रारूपं, "
"Bibtex, &HTML;, अथवा अल्पविरामेन पृथक्कृतानि मूल्यानि (CSV) । निर्यात-आदेशाः वैकल्पिकं "
"तर्कं गृह्णन्ति यत् सङ्ग्रहः वर्तमान-छिद्रे एव सीमितः भवेत् वा न वा इति निर्दिष्टुं ।"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A list of the entry IDs currently selected or being filtered is able to "
"facilitate showing or updating entries in the view."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानकाले चयनितानां अथवा छाननीयानां प्रविष्टीनां ID-सूची दृश्ये प्रविष्टीनां प्रदर्शनं अथवा "
"अद्यतनीकरणं सुलभं कर्तुं समर्था भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A new data file may be opened by using the <command>openFile()</command> "
"command. The full path must be specified."
msgstr ""
"<command>openFile()</command> आदेशस्य उपयोगेन नूतना दत्तांशसञ्चिका उद्घाटिता भवितुम् "
"अर्हति । पूर्णमार्गः अवश्यं निर्दिष्टः भवेत् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A new filter may be set using the <command>setFilter()</command> command, "
"which is the equivalent of typing in the filter box in the main window."
msgstr ""
"<command>setFilter()</command> आदेशस्य उपयोगेन नूतनं फ़िल्टरं सेट् कर्तुं शक्यते, यत् "
"मुख्यविण्डो मध्ये फ़िल्टर पेटीयां टङ्कनस्य समकक्षं भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Given an entry ID, <command>showEntry()</command> will select that entry and "
"show the entry details in the main window."
msgstr ""
"प्रविष्टि-ID दत्तं चेत्, <command>showEntry()</command> तां प्रविष्टिं चित्वा मुख्यविण्डो "
"मध्ये प्रविष्टिविवरणं दर्शयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <constant>Collections</constant> Object"
msgstr "<नित्य>सङ्ग्रहाः</constant> वस्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The full list of &DBus; commands in the <constant>Collections</constant> "
"object is shown below:"
msgstr ""
"&DBus इत्यस्य पूर्णसूची; <constant>Collections</constant> ऑब्जेक्ट् इत्यस्मिन् आदेशाः अधः "
"दर्शिताः सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: advanced.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int addEntry()\n"
"bool removeEntry(int entryID)\n"
"QStringList allValues(QString fieldName)\n"
"QStringList entryValues(int entryID, QString fieldName)\n"
"QStringList selectedBibtexKeys()\n"
"QString entryBibtexKey(int entryID)\n"
"bool setEntryValue(int entryID, QString fieldName, QString value)\n"
"bool addEntryValue(int entryID, QString fieldName, QString value)"
msgstr ""
"int addEntry () 1.1.\n"
"bool removeEntry (int प्रविष्टि आईडी) 1.1.\n"
"QStringList allValues (QString क्षेत्रनाम) 1.1.\n"
"QStringList entryValues (int प्रविष्टिID, QString क्षेत्रनाम)\n"
"QStringList चयनितBibtexKeys () 1.1.\n"
"QString प्रविष्टिBibtexKey (int प्रविष्टि आईडी)\n"
"bool setEntryValue (int entryID, QString क्षेत्रनाम, QString मूल्य)\n"
"bool addEntryValue (int entryID, QString क्षेत्रनाम, QString मूल्य)"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A new empty entry may be created in the current collection using the "
"<command>addEntry()</command> command. The return value is the entry ID, "
"which can then be used to set the field values in the entry. An entry can be "
"deleted from the collection by calling <command>removeEntry()</command>."
msgstr ""
"<command>addEntry()</command> आदेशस्य उपयोगेन वर्तमानसङ्ग्रहे नूतना रिक्तप्रविष्टिः "
"निर्मितुं शक्यते । रिटर्न् मूल्यं प्रविष्टि ID भवति, यस्य उपयोगेन ततः प्रविष्टौ क्षेत्रमूल्यानि "
"सेट् कर्तुं शक्यते । <command>removeEntry()</command> इति आह्वयित्वा संग्रहात् प्रविष्टिः "
"विलोपयितुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Calling <command>allValues()</command> using just a field name will return "
"all the values for that field for the currently selected entries. If no "
"entries are selected, the return list is empty. If an entry ID is included "
"in the command, the field values for that specific entry are returned."
msgstr ""
"केवलं क्षेत्रनाम उपयुज्य <command>allValues()</command> इति आह्वानं "
"वर्तमानचयनितप्रविष्टीनां कृते तस्य क्षेत्रस्य सर्वाणि मूल्यानि प्रत्यागमिष्यति । यदि कोऽपि "
"प्रविष्टिः न चिनोति तर्हि प्रत्यागमनसूची रिक्तं भवति । यदि आदेशे प्रविष्टि-ID समाविष्टं "
"भवति तर्हि तस्य विशिष्टप्रविष्टेः क्षेत्रमूल्यानि प्रत्यागच्छन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the current collection is a bibliography, calling "
"<command>selectedBibtexKeys()</command> will return the Bibtex citation key "
"for all selected entries. The bibtexKey for a specific entry may be found by "
"using the <command>entryBibtexKey()</command> command."
msgstr ""
"यदि वर्तमानसङ्ग्रहः ग्रन्थसूची अस्ति तर्हि <command>selectedBibtexKeys()</command> "
"इति आह्वयित्वा सर्वेषां चयनितप्रविष्टीनां कृते Bibtex उद्धरणकुंजी प्रत्यागमिष्यति । "
"विशिष्टप्रविष्टेः bibtexKey <command>entryBibtexKey()</command> आदेशस्य उपयोगेन "
"प्राप्तुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entries can be edited directly with the &DBus; interface. Given an entry ID, "
"<command>setEntryValue()</command> will set the field value directly. To add "
"a value, without affecting the existing values, use "
"<command>addEntryValue()</command>. The new value gets appended to the end "
"of the existing list."
msgstr ""
"प्रविष्टयः प्रत्यक्षतया &DBus; अन्तरफलकम् । प्रविष्टि-ID दत्तं चेत्, "
"<command>setEntryValue()</command> प्रत्यक्षतया क्षेत्रमूल्यं सेट् करिष्यति । मूल्यं "
"योजयितुं, विद्यमानमूल्यानां प्रभावं विना, <command>addEntryValue()</command> इत्यस्य "
"उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु । नूतनं मूल्यं विद्यमानसूचिकायाः अन्ते संलग्नं भवति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: advanced.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "&DBus; Examples"
msgstr "&DBus; उदाहरणानि"

#. Tag: para
#: advanced.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here are some examples for scripting &appname; using the &DBus; interface. "
"Note that the <command>qdbus</command> command may exist as <command>qdbus-"
"qt5</command> or something similar on your system."
msgstr ""
"अत्र स्क्रिप्टिङ्ग् &appname; &DBus इत्यस्य उपयोगेन; अन्तरफलकम् । ध्यानं कुर्वन्तु यत् "
"<command>qdbus</command> आदेशः भवतः प्रणाल्यां <command>qdbus-qt5</command> इति "
"रूपेण अथवा तत्सदृशं किमपि भवितुम् अर्हति ।"

#. Tag: screen
#: advanced.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Open a Bibtex file</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Tellico org.kde.tellico."
"importBibtex \"/home/robby/reference.bib\" \"replace\"</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>true</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Bibtex सञ्चिकां उद्घाटयन्तु</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Tellico org.kde.tellico."
"importBibtex \"/home/robby/reference.bib\" \"प्रतिस्थापनं\"</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>सत्यम्</computeroutput> इति"

#. Tag: screen
#: advanced.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Export a Bibtex file</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Tellico org.kde.tellico."
"exportBibtex ~/documents/reference.bib</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>true</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Bibtex सञ्चिकां निर्यातयन्तु</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Tellico org.kde.tellico."
"exportBibtex ~/दस्तावेज/सन्दर्भ.bib</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>सत्यम्</computeroutput> इति"

#. Tag: screen
#: advanced.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Export a Bibtex file using the current filter</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Tellico org.kde.tellico."
"exportBibtex ~/documents/reference.bib true</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>true</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>वर्तमानस्य फ़िल्टर</emphasis> इत्यस्य उपयोगेन Bibtex सञ्चिकां निर्यातयन्तु\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Tellico org.kde.tellico."
"exportBibtex ~/दस्तावेज/सन्दर्भ.bib सत्य</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>सत्यम्</computeroutput> इति"

#. Tag: screen
#: advanced.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Echo the citation key of the current selection</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Collections org.kde."
"tellico.selectedBibtexKeys</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>stephenson2004</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>वर्तमानचयनस्य उद्धरणकुंजीम् प्रतिध्वनयन्तु</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /संग्रहः org.kde.tellico."
"selectedBibtexKeys</userinput> इति\n"
"<computeroutput>stephenson2004</computeroutput> इति"

#. Tag: screen
#: advanced.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Add a new entry and set the title</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>myid=`qdbus org.kde.tellico /Collections org."
"kde.tellico.addEntry`</userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /Collections org.kde."
"tellico.setEntryValue $myid title \"My New Book\"</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>true</computeroutput>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>नवीनप्रविष्टिं योजयित्वा शीर्षकं सेट्</emphasis>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>myid=`qdbus org.kde.tellico /संग्रहः org.kde."
"tellico.addEntry`</userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput>qdbus org.kde.tellico /संग्रहाः org.kde.tellico."
"setEntryValue $myid शीर्षकं \"मम नवीनं पुस्तकम्\"</userinput>\n"
"<computeroutput>सत्यम्</computeroutput> इति"
